title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Canada - Cape Bonavista Light
description:
In this video we will fly over Cape Bonavista Light. Cape Bonavista Light is a lighthouse located on Cape Bonavista, Newfoundland. The lighthouse, which operated from 1843 until 1962, is now a provincial museum, containing an exhibition about life in a lighthouse during the 1870s.
